Package com.dua3.meja.model

Interface WorkbookEvent

All Superinterfaces:
Event<Workbook>
All Known Implementing Classes:
WorkbookEvent.ActiveSheetChanged, WorkbookEvent.SheetAdded, WorkbookEvent.SheetRemoved, WorkbookEvent.UriChanged
public interface WorkbookEvent extends Event<Workbook>
Interface representing various events that can occur within a workbook. These events include changes to the active sheet, adding or removing sheets, and changes to the workbook's URI.
